Package: cheese-the-duck
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, python3-pip, libsdl2-2.0-0, libsdl2-mixer-2.0-0, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: imagemagick
Description: A terminal-based virtual pet duck game
 Cheese the Duck is an interactive terminal game where you care for
 your virtual pet duck named Cheese. Features include:
  - AI-powered conversations with your duck
  - Day/night cycles and weather systems
  - Exploration, crafting, and mini-games
  - Duck customization and progression
  - Festival events and achievements
